HipChat
=======

Install Notes
-------------

  1. Auth token - one of your group's API tokens. See: http://www.hipchat.com/docs/api/auth
  2. Room - the full name of the room to send the message to. The room's room_id will also work.

Developer Notes
---------------

data
 - auth_token
 - room_id

payload
  - refer to docs/github_payload
